                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I am not lost and I am not moving. That field past the fence is ours, whatever the sign has been told to say — do not let the sign vote."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I battle travelers for supper money. Two hundred sixty if you beat me, and you will have to mean it. Care to be supper money?"
                        }
                    ],
